Package io.netty.channel

Interface IoOps

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    EpollIoOps, IoUringIoOps, KQueueIoOps, LocalIoOps, NioIoOps
    public interface IoOps
    An IO op that can be submitted to an IoRegistration via IoRegistration.submit(IoOps). // * These submitted IoOps will result in IoEvents on the related IoHandle. Concrete IoRegistration implementations support different concrete IoOps implementations and will so also "produce" concrete IoEvents.
